FBIS4-21010 "jptdd014__l94070" JPRS-TDD-94-014-L JPRS Narcotics 1 April 1994 EAST EUROPE BULGARIA Customs Finds `Narcotic Substance' Aboard Greek Tour Bus Customs Finds `Narcotic Substance' Aboard Greek Tour Bus AU0104113594 Sofia BTA in English 0937 GMT 1 Apr 94 AU0104113594 Sofia BTA English BFN [Text] Petrich, April 1 (BTA) -- About 1,200 [figure as received] kg of some narcotic substance was found in a Greek coach by the customs officers at the Kulata checkpoint on the Bulgarian-Greek border yesterday afternoon. The coach is owned by the Assos Company. Its driver, Repahidis Stilianos, was detained. The case is under investigation.
